summary: Catecoin2.0 ($CATE2) - Catecoin2.0 is a playful and vibrant cryptocurrency project inspired by the beloved cats of Kabosumama, the owner of the iconic Shiba Inu, Kabosu. Featuring Tsutsuji, Ginnan, Oniigiri, and the newest addition, Neiro, Catecoin2.0 aims to bring joy and creativity to the crypto world. It’s a community-driven initiative that celebrates kindness, humor, and the love of cats.
